{"tid":681263,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"請問有無係醫院做或讀緊醫護既人？","createTime":"2018-05-28T01:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T02:14:53.000Z","uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0cd13a960807cc76efe2718580cb105fa03c38d3","tid":681263,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T01:43:49.000Z","msg":"有野想問問<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/094040_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F094040_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f78c2b60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/28/094048_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2F094048_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=daf4b76c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來問上圖個隻藥係出面一般藥房有無得配？<br />\n定都要醫生紙先得？定得醫院先有？<br />\n<br />\n因為本身係醫院開的，但點知佢俾既藥唔夠到覆診個日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時都無時間返醫院拎，除左覆診之外，所以想問最方便出面既藥房有無得配？定一定要返醫院先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eec4a3dd316fb4985897b916209a2db7440d236","tid":681263,"uid":137837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T01:47:52.000Z","msg":"做咗器官移植? 屌仆番醫院拎喇 條命緊要定啲野緊要啊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n利申 唔係讀醫"},{"pid":"93edaf4b806ac350c7c0e6a48927773a1f9dfcc8","tid":681263,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T01:49:46.000Z","msg":"Legal Classification\t:\tPart 1, First &amp; Third Schedules Poison<br />\n<br />\nTacrolimus is used for the prevention of rejection of transplanted kidneys, liver, or heart.<br />\n<br />\n呢隻藥唔係受管制, 所以藥房應理係直買到.<br />\n但呢隻藥似乎係器官移植用架WO, 有返咁上下危險程度<br />\n我反而驚你斷藥會唔會出事, 如果真係到無哂藥果日都買唔到, 即刻死去私家醫院果D 24小時急診搵幫手<br />\n私家醫院就咩藥都有 <img src=\"/asse